reviewText: This DVD is incredibly interesting. I loved it and shared it with friends. Check it out.
These short videos literally were used by God to start a revival in my heart! Watch these with your family and may the Lord stir your heart afresh with love for His Word!

The video was well done, but the contents was shocking.  To see how many men were willing to risk their lives in order to create an accurate version of the Bible in English was so humbling.  We already are sharing this video with other people from our church.
